overview: The user initiated a request for thorough browser-based testing of the
  sleep questionnaire application. The agent began by verifying the dev server
  status and then navigated the application. It tested the main questionnaire
  flow, including attempting manual form filling and utilizing a "Pre-fill &
  Jump to Report (Dev)" button to quickly reach the report section. The PDF
  report generation functionality was successfully tested, and the agent
  confirmed the API call for PDF generation was successful. Additionally, the
  admin login page was tested, and the agent verified that error handling for
  incorrect passwords was working as expected. Throughout the questionnaire
  testing, the agent encountered some confusing navigation behaviors and
  suspected potential React rendering timing issues, where the UI state appeared
  inconsistent with expected navigation outcomes.
